freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Last night - Chills after getting in bed. Today, the other symptoms above, no chills.
Slight dryness of throat/nasal passages when I woke up. Im fine now. Connected? Dont know...

Yesterday, about 2 hours after the shot, I was tired but not excessively so, and a slight off feeling like a little bit of malaise. Went to bed and was fine this morning. No impact to my workout at all this morning, feeling fine today.
